name: Transformers: EarthSpark
overview: The Malto Family’s world turns upside down when the Terrans, the first Earthborn Transformers robots, spark to life. The Terrans will forge an alliance between the human Malto family and the legendary Autobots, uniting them in a shared mission.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: A new generation of Transformers is born, the first to do so on Earth, and find themselves adopted by a human family. As they adapt to their new home, they attempt to find their place in the world amidst the war between the Autobots and Decepticons.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In Season 2, the Emberstone has shattered, and it’s a race against the Decepticons to find all the pieces. Limitless power will be at the fingertips of whoever holds the artifact … Amidst the chaos, Robby meets someone special; Mo uncovers an ancient secret in Witwicky; and the Terrans level up. Together the Malto family and the Autobots see how far they must go to defend all that they love.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: In season three, a giant-size Dome divides the town of Witwicky and traps the Decepticons inside, but it can't hold them forever. The Malto family and the Autobots must figure out a long-term solution, and help arrives from an unlikely place. While doing all they can to get life back to normal again, a mysterious saboteur threatens the Autobots, and Robby and Mo face a ruthless foe who challenges their right to wield the power of Quintus Prime.

episodes.name: Secret Legacy (1) / Secret Legacy (2)
episodes.overview: Robby has trouble adjusting after their family's big move to the rural town of Witwicky, until he and his sister, Mo, discover the first-ever Earthborn Transformers.

episodes.name: Moo-ving In
episodes.overview: As the Malto family get used to its new members, Bumblebee quickly learns that his mission to train the Terrans won't be as easy as he thought.

episodes.name: House Rules
episodes.overview: Thrash is impatient with the family rules and convinces Mo to push their boundaries. But when a Decepticon needs their help, Mo and Thrash find themselves playing by a far more dangerous set of rules.

episodes.name: Classified
episodes.overview: G.H.O.S.T. Special Agent Schloder pursues Twitch after mistaking her for a Deception. Meanwhile, Dot is put through G.H.O.S.T. orientation, where she learns that her employer's intentions may not be what they seem.

episodes.name: Traditions
episodes.overview: Robby backs out of Alex's traditional Wakwak hunt, so Alex shares his family history with Bumblebee, while Twitch, eager to gain her own traditions, encounters "Dad2" - Wheeljack.

episodes.name: Family and Friends
episodes.overview: The Terrans' erratic behavior may be affecting Mo and Robby's anxiety about their first day at their new school. Or it could be something far worse...

episodes.name: Decoy
episodes.overview: While out on a mission to capture three Mini-Cassette bots, Megatron and Optimus Prime have a disagreement about G.H.O.S.T.'s treatment of Decepticons.

episodes.name: Age of Evolution (1) / Age of Evolution (2)
episodes.overview: Twitch and Thrash wonder if they're the only Terrans on Earth. Their family, Optimus Prime, and Bumblebee help seek answers and find new allies! Meanwhile, Mandroid captures Dot and Megatron. Can the larger group become a team and save their friends?

episodes.name: Hashtag: Oops
episodes.overview: Twitch helps Hashtag choose her alt-mode, and it takes them both for a wild and G.H.O.S.T.-ly ride that Bumblebee must help them escape.

episodes.name: Outtakes
episodes.overview: Jawbreaker wonders how to choose the right alt-mode. He interviews other bots on camera to hear their perspectives. But when Hashtag gets involved, Jawbreaker's project loses focus.

episodes.name: Missed Connection
episodes.overview: When Nightshade's feeling isolated from the rest of the Malto family, they find a new connection in the most unlikely of places.

episodes.name: Security Protocols
episodes.overview: Bumblebee's past as an elite racecar driver is exposed and Special Agent Schloder is hot on his trail.

episodes.name: Bear Necessities
episodes.overview: Mother's Day goes wrong and the Maltos discover a toxic threat to Mother Earth.

episodes.name: Warzone
episodes.overview: Robby and Mo join the Terrans on a visit to the Spacebridge Memorial Park, but the memory of the siege opens old wounds...and more...for Megatron.

episodes.name: Home (1) / Home (2)
episodes.overview: The kids and Terrans sneak out for a night of fun in Philadelphia, but their dream of visiting the big city transforms into a nightmare.

episodes.name: A Stygi Situation
episodes.overview: Jawbreaker finally chooses an alt-mode, but instead of changing into it, the alt-mode changes him.

episodes.name: Disarmed
episodes.overview: Robby, Mo, and the Terrans attempt to unlock new Cybersleeve powers, with disastrous results.

episodes.name: What Dwells Within
episodes.overview: The Malto kids are lost in an underground maze of tunnels with a mysterious monster stalking them. To survive, they must team up with Starscream! But can they trust him?

episodes.name: Prime Time
episodes.overview: Feeling helpless as Robby's condition worsens, Mo wishes she had never touched the Emberstone. Quintus Prime shows the young hero that because of her, the world is a better place.

episodes.name: Stowed Away, Stowaways
episodes.overview: Optimus Prime suspects G.H.O.S.T. is hiding something and sends Bumblebee on a secret recon mission deep inside G.H.O.S.T. HQ. The young Maltos sneak in and help their mentor.

episodes.name: The Battle of Witwicky
episodes.overview: The truth about the Terrans is revealed as the Malto family makes a last stand against Croft and her sinister forces within G.H.O.S.T.

episodes.name: Last Hope
episodes.overview: The Malto family must overcome insurmountable odds to stop Mandroid once and for all and save Cybertronian kind.

episodes.name: Aftermath
episodes.overview: One year later… A new Terran is born!

episodes.name: In Ruins
episodes.overview: Mo and Thrash stumble upon ancient ruins and discover a mysterious creature inside.

episodes.name: Control Alt Delete
episodes.overview: Hashtag helps the Autobots get rid of all the old GHOST stuff around base, which has her feeling like her GHOST van alt-mode is obsolete, too. Meanwhile, Shockwave needs to acquire a GHOST hard drive that holds a key to Starscream's master plan.

episodes.name: The Butterfly Effect
episodes.overview: Robby meets his crush, and his siblings feel all his feels at the worst possible time.

episodes.name: Togetherness
episodes.overview: Left behind by his siblings, Jawbreaker finds a new friend and sticks close to him.

episodes.name: Spitfire
episodes.overview: Twitch welcomes a new Terran to the family…

episodes.name: The Imposters
episodes.overview: Spitfire takes from Twitch everything she loves most.

episodes.name: Dude, Where's My Trailer?
episodes.overview: Robby and Hashtag accidentally lose Optimus Prime’s favorite Trailer…

episodes.name: Witwicky
episodes.overview: Mo and Hashtag discover Witwicky’s biggest secret, but Starscream knows about it too…
